    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu wiſſi Moabiteri dsirdeja/ ka tee Kehnini bij zeh-wichees prett teem karroht/ tad tappe tee tafankti wiſſi/ kas us Apbrunnofchann gann wezzi/ un wehl wezzati bija/ un stahjahs us to Rohbeschu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad tee Rihta agri zehlahs/ un ta Saule pahr to Uhdem bija uslehkuſi/ tad re-dseja tee Moabiteri itt ka buhtu tas Uhdens prett teem tik far-kans/ ka Affins.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee tazzija: Schis irr Affins/ tee Kehnint irr ar fatwu paschu Sobbinu maitajschees/ un irr zitts zittu nokawis. Un un Moab/ zellees us Laupt-schann.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet kad tee pee Israëka Lehgera nahze/ tad zehlehs tee Israëliteri/ un kawe tohs Moa-biterus/ un tee behdse preeksch winneem. Ta nahze tee eekſch (tabs Semmes)/ un kawe tohs Moabiterus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee nolauszja tohs Pilfsahtus/ un iffatrs nette fa wus Akminus us wiſſem lab-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nn tas Moab-Kehninsch redſeja/ ka ta Kan-na wiſſai gruhta bija/ tad me wiſſch feptieſtints Wi pee jewis/ kas to Sobbinu wilke/ ka wiſſch zaurlant prett to Eedomiteru Kehni bet tee ne spehje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehme wiſſch pirmdſinnmſchun Dedlu/ kan wiſſa Weeta par Kehntan ka un uppureja to par Dedsa uppurit us to Muhti. Zar apskattahs Israëls lohti/ un stahjehs no ta/ un greeſahs pakkat tawa Semme.\n"
